{"code":"ERR_BAD_REQUEST","config":{"adapter":["xhr","http","fetch"],"allowAbsoluteUrls":true,"data":"{\"model\":\"deepseek-chat\",\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"system\",\"content\":\"You are a helpful assistant that summarizes documents. \\n              Return a JSON object with exactly this structure:\\n              {\\n                \\\"brief\\\": \\\"string (2-3 sentences)\\\",\\n                \\\"mainPoints\\\": [\\\"string\\\", \\\"string\\\", ...] (3-5 bullet points),\\n                \\\"keyPhrases\\\": [\\\"string\\\", \\\"string\\\", ...] (5-10 key terms)\\n              }\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Please summarize the following document.\\n\\nProvide a brief overview, 3-5 main points, and 5-10 key phrases.\\n\\nDocument:\\nHussien Zoughaib\\nBeirut, Lebanon\\nPhone: +961 78818955\\nEmail: [your-email@example.com]\\nLinkedIn: linkedin.com/in/hussien-\\nGitHub: github.com/Hussiendev\\nDate: March 10, 2026\\nHiring Committee\\nAspire Software\\nBeirut, Lebanon\\nApplication for Mid Software Developer Position\\nDear Hiring Committee,\\nI am writing to express my strong interest in the Mid Software Developer position at Aspire\\nSoftware. With my solid foundation in full-stack development and hands-on experience integrat-\\ning AI technologies, I am confident in my ability to contribute effectively to your development\\nteam.\\nIn my recent project, Study Spark App, I developed a full-stack application that demonstrates\\nmy technical capabilities:\\n• Frontend: Built with React and TypeScript\\n• Backend: Developed using Node.js and Express.js\\n• AI Integration: Implemented ChatGPT-4 API to create an intelligent chatbot that eval-\\nuates student responses\\n• Current Work: Integrating DeepSeek API for PDF summarization with custom-trained\\ncriteria\\nWhat makes me a strong candidate for this role:\\n• Technical Versatility: Proficiency in JavaScript, TypeScript, Java, C, and modern\\nframeworks\\n• AI Experience: Practical experience with AI integrations and API implementations\\n• Full-Stack Capabilities: Ability to work across the entire development lifecycle\\n• Immediate Availability: Ready to start immediately and work Eastern Time Zone hours\\nI am particularly drawn to Aspire Software’s reputation for innovation and would welcome the\\nopportunity to bring my AI integration experience and development skills to your team. I am\\nLebanese, based in Beirut, and fully prepared to commit to the responsibilities of this role.\\nYou can review my code and project architecture here:\\n• Study Spark Client Repository\\n1\\n• Study Spark Server Repository\\nThank you for considering my application. I look forward to the possibility of discussing how\\nmy skills and experience align with Aspire Software’s goals. I am available for an interview at\\nyour convenience.\\nSincerely,\\nHussien Zoughaib\\nlinkedin.com/in/hussien-\\n+961 78818955\\n2\"}],\"temperature\":0.3,\"max_tokens\":1000,\"response_format\":{\"type\":\"json_object\"}}","env":{},"headers":{"Accept":"application/json, text/plain, */*","Accept-Encoding":"gzip, compress, deflate, br","Authorization":"Bearer sk-e6c25806e5b7447e98a4ec0199a93bc0","Content-Length":"2810","Content-Type":"application/json","User-Agent":"axios/1.13.4"},"maxBodyLength":-1,"maxContentLength":-1,"method":"post","timeout":0,"transformRequest":[null],"transformResponse":[null],"transitional":{"clarifyTimeoutError":false,"forcedJSONParsing":true,"silentJSONParsing":true},"url":"https://api.deepseek.com/v1/chat/completions","xsrfCookieName":"XSRF-TOKEN","xsrfHeaderName":"X-XSRF-TOKEN"},"isAxiosError":true,"level":"error","message":"DeepSeek API error: Request failed with status code 402","name":"AxiosError","request":{"_closed":true,"_contentLength":2810,"_defaultKeepAlive":true,"_ended":true,"_events":{},"_eventsCount":7,"_hasBody":true,"_header":"POST /v1/chat/completions HTTP/1.1\r\nAccept: application/json, text/plain, */*\r\nContent-Type: application/json\r\nAuthorizatio